---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About BenefitsCheck UK"
  description="BenefitsCheck UK is a free, independent benefit checking tool for working parents. Updated for 2026/27 rates."
>
  <div style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 2rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">
    <a href="/" style="font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1f;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">← Back to checker</a>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;color:#1a1a1a;margin:1.5rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.2;">About BenefitsCheck UK</h1>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">BenefitsCheck UK is a free, independent tool that helps working parents find out which benefits they may be entitled to. It was built because most existing benefits calculators are long, complicated, and designed for everyone — not specifically for people in work with children.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">Our checker covers 7 key benefits that working families most commonly miss: Universal Credit, Child Benefit, Free School Meals, Tax-Free Childcare, Free Childcare Hours, Healthy Start Vouchers, and Council Tax Reduction.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">All calculations use 2026/27 DWP and HMRC rates. Results are estimates only — your actual entitlement is determined by DWP and HMRC based on a full assessment.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">Nothing you enter is stored, tracked, or shared. All calculations happen entirely in your browser.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">Disclaimer</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">This tool provides estimates only and is not financial advice. Always verify your entitlement on GOV.UK or with Citizens Advice before making any claim decisions.</p>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#888;margin-top:2rem;">Rates last verified: April 2026</p>
  </div>
</Base>
